@startuml
!theme plain
actor User
participant "SolidJS UI" as SolidJS
participant "Ktor Server" as Ktor
participant "Bash Orchestrator" as Bash
participant "State Analyzer" as Analyzer
participant "Strategy Agent" as Strategy
participant "Dialogue Agent" as Dialogue
participant "Kotlin Tools (Validator/Bridge)" as Tools
participant "Stockfish" as Stockfish

== Hint Request Flow ==
User -> SolidJS: Clicks "Get Hint"
SolidJS -> Ktor: GET /api/hint
Ktor -> Tools: Get Top 3 Moves (FEN, MultiPV=3)
Tools -> Stockfish: position fen ... \n go depth 15
Stockfish --> Tools: info ... pv e4 ... \n info ... pv d4 ... \n info ... pv Nf3 ...
Tools --> Ktor: [ "e4 (+0.5)", "d4 (+0.4)", "Nf3 (+0.3)" ]
Ktor --> SolidJS: Returns hints
SolidJS -> User: Displays Top 3 lines

== Replayability Flow ==
User -> SolidJS: Clicks "Previous Move"
SolidJS -> Ktor: GET /api/history?move=-1
Ktor -> Ktor: Read PGN, calculate past FEN
Ktor --> SolidJS: Return historical FEN
SolidJS -> User: Renders past state

== Standard Move Flow (Coach Response) ==
User -> SolidJS: Drags Piece (e2 to e4)
SolidJS -> Ktor: POST /api/move { "move": "e4" }
Ktor -> Bash: ProcessBuilder("bash", "orchestrator.sh", "e4").start()

note over Bash, Stockfish: Bash Orchestration Loop Starts

Bash -> Tools: Validate Human Move ("e4")
Tools -> Stockfish: Verify Legality
Stockfish --> Tools: Valid
Tools --> Bash: Move Valid
Bash -> Bash: Update FEN & PGN

note over Bash, Stockfish: LLM Coaching Turn Begins

Bash -> Analyzer: Analyze Current FEN
Analyzer -> Tools: Get Evaluation (FEN)
Tools -> Stockfish: eval
Stockfish --> Tools: score cp 45
Tools --> Analyzer: Evaluation (+0.45)
Analyzer -> Strategy: Context: "Solid opening by user, slight edge."

Strategy -> Strategy: Generate Candidate Coach Moves (SAN)
Strategy -> Tools: Validate Candidates
Tools -> Stockfish: check legality
Stockfish --> Tools: Valid
Tools --> Strategy: Valid

Strategy -> Bash: Selects Move (e.g. "e5")

Bash -> Dialogue: Generate Advice (User="e4", Opponent="e5", Eval="+0.45")
Dialogue --> Bash: "Good center control. I'll play e5 to challenge it."

Bash -> Bash: Update FEN & PGN

note over Bash, Stockfish: Bash Orchestration Loop Ends

Bash --> Ktor: Process Exits (Code 0)
Ktor -> Ktor: Read updated game_state.fen
Ktor --> SolidJS: HTTP 200 OK { fen: "rnbqk...", dialog: "Good center control..." }
SolidJS -> User: Renders Board & Coach Advice

@enduml
